TOP_SEA_LEVEL = Elevation of highest point above sea level (NAVD88) one decimal place

ELEVATION_GROUND_LEVEL = Elevation of roofline edge above ground level (NAVD88) one decimal place

TOP_GROUND_LEVEL = Elevation of highest point above ground level (NAVD88) one decimal place
